{"tid":109973,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得La la land中文字幕翻譯唔係幾準","createTime":"2017-02-06T10:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T04:24:45.000Z","uid":61117,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d45871988bd892466d73abf6d3385264a26a5c7b","tid":109973,"uid":61117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"利申我鍾意套戲，唔係特登想逢紅必反，但邊睇邊覺得(舒琪譯既)中文字幕翻譯，同套戲本身既對白內容好似有d出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇翻譯同好一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1，someone in the crowd，emma stone係搵緊賞識佢既知音人，唔係翻譯所講既意中人。Crowd就譯左做&quot;眾生&quot;，如果直譯&quot;人海&quot;既話好似更有&quot;億個背影但和你碰上&quot;既感覺<br />\n<br />\n2，&quot;It's another day of sun&quot;呢句，舒琪類似譯左做&quot;陽光伴你再闖蕩&quot;，但如果直譯做&quot;明天又是新一天&quot;甚至&quot;在晴朗的一天再出發&quot;，好似更加直接傳遞到個意思<br />\n<br />\n3，a lovely night，係男女主歡喜冤家式對唱，其中一句：<br />\nMia：And though you looked so cute in your polyester suit<br />\n<br />\nSebastian：It's wool<br />\n<br />\n字幕譯左做類似&quot;雖然你著住套靚西裝&quot;咁既意思，同下句男主回應&quot;羊毛&quot;唔係好做到互寸既味道。<br />\n<br />\n4，不過有d都譯得幾好，例如&quot;The ripples from pebbles&quot;譯左做：一石擊起千重浪<br />\n<br />\n最後重點：emma stone世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dd1384dffac31d0cd1a1a219f85b64041dcb78","tid":109973,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"睇字幕果陣，睇到辭不達意<br />\n不過一dd姐<br />\n利申 : Emma Stone I love you!!!"},{"pid":"7d90d2b4d3ec85a9d2c45bdc15dc33a5cbd1440e","tid":109973,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申我鍾意套戲，唔係特登想逢紅必反，但邊睇邊覺得(舒琪譯既)中文字幕翻譯，同套戲本身既對白內容好似有d出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇翻譯同好一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji